      "text": "eemanto to Senunt/ ko es winnu\nTehweem swchreijß efinu win-\nneem doht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad Israëls/ ko praf-\nfa tas KUNGS taws Deews\nno tewis/ bes ka to KUNGU\ntawu Deewu bihtees/ wiſſos\nwinna Zeltòß staigaht/ un winnu\nmihleht/ un tam KUNGA M\ntawam Deewam kalpoht/ no\nwiſſas tawas Sirõs/ un no wiſ-\nfas tawas Dwehfeles.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Baufiusun\nwinna Liffkumus turreht/ ko es\njums ſchodeen pawehtu: Tew par\nlabut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redſt/ tam KUNGAM\ntawam Deewam peederr Debbes\nun to Debbeſchu Debbeſis/ ta\nSeine/un wiſſ kas eekſch tahßirr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr pee taweem Teh-\nweein ween irr tam KUNGAM\nlabs Prahts bijiß/ winnuß mih-\nleht/ un irr winnu Dsimmunnu\npehz winneem/ juhs paſchus/\nno wiſſeem Laudim isredſejs/ itt\nka tas ſchodeen irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Apgraisajt tad juhfas\nSirõs Prec̀kch-Ahdu/ un ne ef-\nsat wairs pahrgalwigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas KUNGS juhſu\nDeews irr weens Deews to Dee-\nwu/ un weens KUNGS to\nRungu/ TAS STIPRAJS\nDEEWS/ tas leelajs/ tas war-\nrenajs/ un tas zeenamajs/ kas ne\nkahda Waign usluhko neds Dah-\nwanas nemm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un darra Teefu tam Bah-\nistan/ un tahm Atraitnehin/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "mihto to Sweschineeku/ un dohd\nwinnam Maisi un Drebbes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz buhs jums to\nSweschineeku mihtcht/ jo juhs\neffat Sweschineeki bijufschi Egip-\ntes-Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To KUNGU tawu Dee-\nwu buhs tew bihtees/ winnam\nkalpoht/ un winnam peekehrtees/\nun pee winna Wahrdaswehreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſch irr tawa Teik-\nſchana/ un wiſſch irr taws\nDeews/ kas pee tew fehihs leelas\nun zeenamas Leetas Darrijs irr/\nko tawas Azzis irr redſejſchas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawi Tehwi nogahje uhe\nEgiptes-Semini ſeptinxdefinite\nDwehfeles(Pulkâ)/un nu irr ta-\nKUNGS taws Deewstew wai\nrojs itt ka tahß Debbes Swaig-\nsnes Pulkâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ad buhs nutew to KUN-\nGU tawu Deewu mih-\nleht/ un turreht winna\nBauslibas/ un winnaLiffkumus\nun winna Teefas/ un winna\nPatvehlefchanas wiſſu Muhschu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un jums buhs ſchodeen sin-\nnaht/ ka es ne (runnaju) ar juh-\nfeem Behrneem/ kas to ne finna/\nun kas ne irr redſejſchi ta KUN-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
